#: ui/screens/end_screen/EndScreen.tscn
msgid "They’re a great way to pick up specific game mechanics but they’re not as effective when you’re trying to learn new skills from the ground up."
msgstr "그것들은 특정 게임 메커니즘을 익히는 데는 아주 좋은 방법이지만, 새로운 기술을 기초부터 배우려 할 때는 그만큼 효과적이지 않습니다."

